What is Orpheus?

Orpheus is an adventure game that incorporates theology and philosophy.

 

The game is about the alien attack in the medieval world. and in this context, it offers its religious and philosophical teachings to the user. It has an unprecedented scenario in the Turkish game industry.

Scenario, map design and mission chart

It emerges as a result of philosophical imagination and creativity

Storyboard, musics additional animations

Used Blender, FL Studio and Da Vinci Resolve

What stage is the game at?

In the game, the map design is renewed. The assignments of the game scenario are being worked on. We also have a great deal of unfulfilled responsibilities when it comes to coding. But we don't let that stop us.

What is Craedu?

CRAEDU is a new generation education platform. Developed with Unreal Engine and VR technologies, it adds a new perspective to the education life of individuals.

With CRAEDU, you can get the experience you want in the virtual world by getting the hands-on training you need, wherever and whenever you want.

What areas do we focus on?

  1. In vocational education, the inability of applied training to adequately meet the needs of the sector.

  2. Difficulty in finding a job for individuals who have studied for many years.

  3. Individuals find it difficult to pursue a career in areas of their abilities and interests.

What do we offer?

More

  1. A detailed and concentrated training atmosphere from the most basic to advanced.

  2. Realistic experience opportunities that prepare you for the professional world and the sector.

  3. Additional income and networking opportunities for individuals who produce and learn.
